metadata.name: Weird Flowers - Mutuus Consensus
metadata.description:
Weird Flowers, No. 42 

Since the beginning of the pandemic I started illustrating vague, imaginary flowers. Exotic, dreamy flower species were given semi-Latin names - Hopeful, affirmative, relevant to present times, and our rather universal problems and hopes.

1/1

4244 x 6000 px
